1. *Tebe* se prisetim uvek kad vidim sunce. (I always remember you when I see the sun.)
2. Ja ne znam *tebe*. (I don't know you.)
3. *Tebi* se divim zbog tvoje hrabrosti. (I admire you for your courage.)
4. *Tebe* ne mogu da zamislim bez nje. (I can't imagine you without her.)
5. Ona misli da je *tebi* sve dozvoljeno. (She thinks that everything is allowed to you.)
6. *Tebi* ne mogu da verujem. (I can't believe you.)
7. On je bio ponosan na *tebe*. (He was proud of you.)
8. Nemam vremena da se igram sa *tebom*. (I don't have time to play with you.)